- 400 Bad Request
- 401 Unauthorized
- 404 Not Found
- 500 Server Error

### 3. Performance Testing
```bash
ab -n 100 -c 10 http://localhost:3000/api/endpoint
```

### 4. Security Validation
- SQL Injection attempts
- XSS attempts
- Auth bypass attempts

